dbExecute(observational_db, "CREATE TABLE plants (
date varchar(5) NOT NULL,
site_id varchar(10) NOT NULL,
line char(1),
direction varchar(50),
point varchar(2), 
top_code varchar(6), 
code_1 varchar(6), 
code_2 varchar(6), 
code_3 varchar(6), 
soil_surface varchar(5), 
PRIMARY KEY (site_id)
);")
